Project Plan – Trusted Home Services Platform

Phase 1: Research

Look at existing service apps in Pakistan.

Decide which services to start with (plumber, electrician, AC repair, maid).

Talk to potential users to understand their needs (trust, safety, quick service).

Phase 2: Design

Make a simple mobile app and website.

Create a worker onboarding process (ID check, background check).

Design booking flow: select service → choose time → confirm.

Phase 3: Development

Build core features:

User registration & login

Worker registration & verification

Service booking system

Reviews & ratings

Add extra features:

Emergency booking (30–60 min arrival)

Payment options (cash + online)

Phase 4: Testing

Test booking flow with sample users.

Test worker verification process.

Check emergency response speed.

Phase 5: Launch

Launch in one city first (e.g., Lahore).

Collect feedback from users.

Improve based on reviews.

Phase 6: Expansion

Add more cities (Karachi, Islamabad).

Add more services (carpenter, painter, etc.).

Offer subscription plans for regular home maintenance.

Success Goals

Onboard many verified workers.

Maintain high user ratings (4.5+ stars).

Emergency response under 45 minutes.

Increase repeat bookings.